<strong>Studio Album, released in 2011</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;"><br>1. The Surgical Cut, Parts 2-4  (9:51)    <br>2. Departure  (4:41)    <br>3. DesIre  (12:08)    <br>4. Wintersong  (5:23)    <br>5. The Illusion (Death Is Dead)  (6:19)    <br>6. The Surgical Cut, Part 1  (9:04)    <br>7. Epilogue: For The Love Of Ghosts  (1:46)  <br><br>Total Time  49:12<br><br></p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- Markus Bratusa / guitars, vocals, programming, additional keyboards<br>- Arthur Darnhofer-Demar / bass, backing vocals<br>- Nick Koch / drums, programming<br><br>Collaborators:<br>- Christoph W. Pirker / keyboards, organ (1-6) <br>- Markus Czwiertnia / violin (4) <br>- Peter Yearsley and Librivox / spoken words (1 & 6) <br><br></p>


